title: Gorgonzola-cream pasta sauce
description: creamy pasta sauce
source: sohalt
categories:
  - main-course
  - pasta
ingredients:
  - name: gorgonzola
    qty: 200g
  - name: heavy creame
    qty: 200g
  - name: onion
    qty: 1 pcs
  - name: red pepper flakes
preparation:
  - name: making sauce
    prep:
      - dice onions, saute in olive oil untill soft
      - add cream, and then add gorgonzola
      - stir until cheese is melted
      - add red pepper flakes
      - season with salt and pepper

      
      
